Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就当是赠品啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新品种的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥末味大蒜和肉汤乳酪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的人还挺多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了  总这么照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦  春香你也经常光顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我给放哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池的入场券
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  邻镇不是新建了个温水游泳池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也没小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟夏奈和千秋一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  一起开开心心地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:17.72,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第8碗  游泳池是同父异母的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  好啊  泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天特地跑去游泳这种怪事  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就人类干得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周才开张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有点想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回记得跟大婶道谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我一直都觉得点心店的大婶很能干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就决定周六去游泳池吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶紧招人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  再来一杯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是  什么事？春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喝茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  是内田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳哦  去游泳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你要穿哪件泳衣去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:36.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（如何学会游泳）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（旱鸭子同盟～让你也能学会游泳～）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  人员决定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕是在看黄色网页吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真在黄色网站上用黄色工具收集黄色图片吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你都叫谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先叫了内田和冬马  还有阿珍和吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一个叫谁好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊  这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  叔叔  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待去泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿什么泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说  有没有那种转啊转的滑梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太勉为其难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是温水的  也只是酒店的泳池而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…  这样啊  有点失望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知足吧  这季节能去游泳就很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要去游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天也就算了  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候没必要特地跑去泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢泳池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又没说不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是提出个常识性的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧  我要穿新买的泳衣去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还特地买新的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在买的话  再穿可就得等到夏天了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  去年盂兰盆节结束时候买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里人却说什么海水浴已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  周六的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  我该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  该不该去泳池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫的是阿珍…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周末你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢  我有两张游泳池的票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  邻镇新建的酒店附带的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话  我想咱们一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我客气什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那周六在我家门口会合  早上九点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  都有谁一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹们啦  还有几个千秋的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一来  泳衣就没人欣赏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  说什么呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香要去游泳池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  也就是说不需要我帮忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子排球部刚刚决定于本周六进行特别训练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是穿连身式的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想辜负大家期望  应该穿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不辜负谁的期望啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你这哪儿买的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的秘诀是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树立远大的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知很鲁莽  但仍对自己充满信心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会实现的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信念正是力量来源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  藤冈  你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  向泳池前进吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么近还要特意麻烦你送我们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿  反正我也很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车一会儿就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都带泳衣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接穿过来了  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真新颖啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…忘穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在她们三人心中到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来夏奈很喜欢你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要2吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对哦  是3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢我吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我还以为被她讨厌呢  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么受鬼牌喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来她喜欢我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  好好看地图吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个  我们这是往哪儿开？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…当然是邻镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  只不过是去邻镇  还要开多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要…两小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发的时候你也是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到刚到这里就到午饭时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上花了不少时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健叔真是一到关键时候就掉链子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之接下来才是重点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把上午耽误的一口气补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要游到25米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游给你们看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到泳池了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈  她哪儿来的干劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么想来泳池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？没看出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校时候看她没什么兴趣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游泳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看起来干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实她很喜欢游泳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？但是好像没见过千秋游泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  估计她不想让人知道会游泳这件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋是从亚马逊的黑色三角州中跑出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谁是半鱼人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  来陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？可我还没吃完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真老实啊  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能违抗任性公主的旨意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋被班上一部分男生叫作公主  很有威信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些女生也这么叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋是公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  本泳池还合您心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起生活了十多年我居然都没意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完体操了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  你说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？稍微说了点关于公主的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  勿动怒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  做完体操了吗  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  您这是要去哪儿  要拿泳圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  还不呈上泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦一下  请给我一个公主用的泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  吉野侍从长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  公主  要去厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去厕所的话  就让内田代劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  让我代替千秋去厕所  还是很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还是去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人可是公主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…怎么了突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在本公主要把所有笨蛋都流放到孤岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝是个什么东西？笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那汝为何生得一副蠢面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说「你」  真是无礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我「公主」！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋已经驾轻就熟了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不用阻止她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是在玩儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐都嫌麻烦直接装做不认识她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在睡觉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次  差不多该下水了吧  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  过来帮本公主一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴好好拉着我  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是在跟谁说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  千秋  脚能踩到底的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤冈  别妨碍我们特训啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是要有这决心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香要是出了什么事  我会马上冲过去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  为了确保南春香呼吸畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给南春香进行人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你在干什么啊  打工小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标是  今年夏天能游25米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  这种想法或许说这种气势才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那千秋你现在能游多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现在能游多少没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是  在夏天时候能游到25米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连这么一点都游不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用梦幻之自由泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标就那么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  你听好  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你不游了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标要定得远大些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知很鲁莽  但仍对自己充满信心  就一定会实现的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信念正是力量来源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  那段话真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标是公主抱！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋说鲁莽的目标可以靠信念来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才定得远大些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…唉？再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要被人公主抱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像千秋那样溺水的话  也许会有人这样来救你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那我就在这里假装溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是真溺水了  我可救不了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点儿想尿尿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能尿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标  将这个朋友引向正途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这样真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是标准的自由泳姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的能游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  应该不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐  我在对面发现春香了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  速水前辈  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今天的社团活动要在泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们女子排球部  今天的目标就是「捕获」！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  「捕获」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  春香在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一旁睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是来干什么的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你这里是小孩子用的泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让…让我休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  人工呼吸…哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～还挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  不过果然有很多情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了  今年的目标是拉近和藤冈之间的距离！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到了夏天就能两个人相伴去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…哪儿有那么顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是藤冈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标…实现！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在…游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮一下她比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎她本人觉得是在游
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着倒像是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿抱着膝盖干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不下水游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想  穿成怎么就没人发现我是男生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈他也是  看到我穿这样  还以为我是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须趁这机会纠正这个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  想让他注意你的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  藤冈的事就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的目标  极力避开藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经通过自主训练找到感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就游25米的泳池太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  自由泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点儿恐怖电影的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好远…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么远…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到…还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈？！那就是终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是25米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了  夏奈！终于游了25米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会站在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是想救我那可爱的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！千…千秋！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？夏奈  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的心灵好像受到了重创
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不问发生什么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:20:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  身后的利子怎么这么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像是…心病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  今天到你们家玩儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓  你们问过春香了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我也一起去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我们也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好多客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我定好目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建一座能容下一百人的大房子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规模够大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  扔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望世界和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位喜欢吃鲣鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月到六月能抓到的是鲣鱼幼苗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九月到十月能抓到的是回流鲣鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回流鲣鱼就是当初没抓的鲣鱼幼苗的成鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用油一炸很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲣鱼幼苗做成鱼干  回流的做成生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是时令的精髓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:44.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第9碗  「难以掩饰了吧？阿珍的秘密」
